Package com.veeva.generic.keywords

Class GenericKeywords

java.lang.Object
com.veeva.generic.keywords.GenericKeywords
All Implemented Interfaces:
NonSeleniumKeywords, SeleniumKeywords
public class GenericKeywords extends Object implements SeleniumKeywords, NonSeleniumKeywords
GenericKeywords is a class that implements the SeleniumKeywords and NonSeleniumKeywords interfaces. It provides various utility methods and includes operations like clicking, entering text, taking screenshots, and more.
